Created an Usuario class with its own file.
Created an Admin class which inherited parameters from the Usuario class.

The index.php file called the Admin class from Admin.php file and showed the output in a simple html page with no css for design.

To see the output I used the terminal to cd into the folder where these project its and then used: 
    php -S localhost:8000
After that i used http://localhost:8000/index.php on my browser to check the output.